{"id": 1494, "genre": 1001, "title": "你心目中的理想上司应该有什么样的特点？", "description": "总之不是三天两头跟我“谈理想”那种。（题图来自：Elliot Kruszynski）", "record_count": 5398, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170210154448dOQpG7T3Z1UvFP46.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-13T03:00:25Z", "options": [{"id": 166400, "content": "给员工体面的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935629}, {"id": 166656, "content": "拜托，不要画饼了。大家都不是三岁小孩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936721}, {"id": 167424, "content": "很简单，跟我合得来！", "image": "img/option/option/20170216142738Re2ClIrxc8fKTQaD", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938285}, {"id": 166145, "content": "只是单纯上下级关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903109}, {"id": 166401, "content": "不情绪化，理智", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933008}, {"id": 167170, "content": "专业技能比我厉害两个级别", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 171778, "content": "犯了错就特别凶\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870633}, {"id": 166147, "content": "天生的领导人气质，没办法就是这么帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913581}, {"id": 166404, "content": "好好说话，说有用的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277107}, {"id": 166406, "content": "不要总画大饼和甩锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930002}, {"id": 166151, "content": "必须平等待人:我干活挣钱又不是欠你钱丫别跟我阴阳怪气的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907657}, {"id": 166407, "content": "有原则有底线有责任心，有能力更要有人品。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929173}, {"id": 166408, "content": "有能力管我 \n不没事儿找事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933995}, {"id": 166153, "content": "整天忽悠，画饼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229414}, {"id": 166665, "content": "懂得体谅，态度好(✪▽✪)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918475}, {"id": 166154, "content": "跟着他能赚到钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778598}, {"id": 166410, "content": "一视同仁，管理能力强，下属才能服你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832637}, {"id": 168970, "content": "有话直说 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871139}, {"id": 170252, "content": "跟我保持距离和上下级关系，别一天到晚提议搞活动搞得拒绝也尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945562}, {"id": 166414, "content": "懂得欣赏和尊重每个员工", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934626}, {"id": 166415, "content": "请实在一些。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934502}, {"id": 166160, "content": "不要总谈鸡汤，多做点实事。另外，不要贪污下属钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686544}, {"id": 166416, "content": "要让下属守规矩，首先自己就要守；不啰嗦，不讲起他下属的坏话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 167184, "content": "放手去做吧，出了事我扛著，神一般的存在……", "image": "img/option/option/20170215223422PTJYCGsXnz9VUxbK.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937731}, {"id": 166161, "content": "有热情，有能力，会教东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935068}, {"id": 171025, "content": "负责有态度热心，请假适当给放！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947423}, {"id": 166162, "content": "知道什么是重要的事，并坚持做对。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 166418, "content": "说话算话，只要不把年终奖变成“年中奖”我都还能接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935682}, {"id": 166163, "content": "不要逞强 什么都出头 下面的人很累啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905305}, {"id": 166419, "content": "有逻辑，有远见", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933993}, {"id": 167955, "content": "外里护短，内里教导", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939468}, {"id": 172051, "content": "第一:按时吃药，按时发薪，履行合约。第二:不放屁，不扯谈，不记仇。第三:不要君主制度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908237}, {"id": 166164, "content": "有用脑用心，专业能力要比我强，不谈情怀不谈理想，在位时帮我们争取利益，对内可以骂成狗，对外要袒护，分手时好聚好散，多替下属着想，最好不贪小便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394252}, {"id": 166421, "content": "长得好看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 15371}, {"id": 167445, "content": "温和有礼，循循善诱，才华横溢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930845}, {"id": 166166, "content": "接地气，不会的动手教", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930958}, {"id": 166422, "content": "让我时刻觉得我还年轻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798356}, {"id": 166678, "content": "不当员工的监视器，不一直盯着员工做事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936843}, {"id": 166167, "content": "专业、就事论事", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660621}, {"id": 166168, "content": "生活是生活，工作是工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356859}, {"id": 166169, "content": "逻辑思维要正常", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907243}, {"id": 166681, "content": "就事论事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936857}, {"id": 166170, "content": "做事果断，错了承担", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 166426, "content": "有眼光能力强 不要提出很渣的想法还问我怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 166171, "content": "跟着他能学到东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891172}, {"id": 166427, "content": "有颜值 無官腔 关爱下属", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905397}, {"id": 166683, "content": "谈钱伤感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936908}, {"id": 170267, "content": "胸怀宽广", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943147}, {"id": 166172, "content": "不要每天打感情牌～", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913452}, {"id": 166428, "content": "有规划，理智！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935732}]}